<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I swear people full of so much Bs...<BR>
<BR>
Anyways many people have said this but I got the parts just messin around so I went ahead and did the quest (bought the spell of course)<BR>
<BR>
Fire goblin skin<BR>
From a regular Fire Goblin in solA (maybe more but that is where i got mine)<BR>
Ice goblin skin<BR>
Ice Goblin Elite Guard (or something like that, spawns near king, drop is about 1 in 6)<BR>
The skin ONLY drops from elite guards, trust me on that, cleared perma many many times.<BR>
Twice Woven Cloak<BR>
faerie guard in lesser fay, fairly common, 1 in 3 or 4<BR>
Scroll of Elemental Armor<BR>
Bought at most mage guilds (prolly all) cost me about 20pp with 136 charisma and indiff faction, no way it is 80, and you must be ugly for it to be 38 =)<BR>
<BR>
Get all those, turn them into Joyce<BR>
<BR>
Exp for the quest was fairly good, got about 1/5 a bub at lvl 35 (Hell lvl)<BR>
<BR>
Hope this helps, and all these facts are just that, facts.<BR>
<BR>
Dalborn the Great</font></td></tr></table>
