<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Darondal</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-18 16:47:16</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have camped perma for the past few of weekends and I know it is really rare, but I got my ice Goblin pelt off of an Ice Goblin while camping the Preacher.  I figure over the last few weekends, the group I have been with must've killed anywhere from 100 to 200 Gobs in there who weren't casters.  Out of all that time, we found only one other pelt on the Ice Goblins.  And both were definitely Ice Goblins...never seen one on a caster.  We didn't camp the King's room, so we really didn't see any of the elites, but I think from what others in Perma have said that they almost always drop the pelts.<BR>
<BR>
Be safe my friends<BR>
D</font></td></tr></table>
